  "detailed_description": "<strong>Not Alone</strong> is a first-person mystical horror game where you need to escape from a terrifying house. This house may look familiar to some, but that's only at first glance. Read the notes to understand what happened and search for ways to escape.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2928740/extras/88f088156790daf96e25899bb4a48a97.poster.avif?t=1715160700\" width=690 height=388 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2928740/extras/88f088156790daf96e25899bb4a48a97.webm?t=1715160700\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2928740/extras/88f088156790daf96e25899bb4a48a97.mp4?t=1715160700\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>Gameplay:</strong><br>The player will have to explore an unfamiliar mansion and uncover the story of a young family that recently moved in here. The player is immersed in an oppressive atmosphere and constantly feels that someone is watching him. Find keys, move through new locations, and discover more details of the frightening story. And yes, try to get out of that scary house.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2928740/extras/f8ef5ed351f4163e0029358377f3b9b9.poster.avif?t=1715160700\" width=690 height=388 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2928740/extras/f8ef5ed351f4163e0029358377f3b9b9.webm?t=1715160700\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2928740/extras/f8ef5ed351f4163e0029358377f3b9b9.mp4?t=1715160700\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>Game Features:</strong><br>• The frightening story.<br>• Atmospheric locations.<br>• The feeling of a familiar place.",
  "about_the_game": "<strong>Not Alone</strong> is a first-person mystical horror game where you need to escape from a terrifying house. This house may look familiar to some, but that's only at first glance. Read the notes to understand what happened and search for ways to escape.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2928740/extras/88f088156790daf96e25899bb4a48a97.poster.avif?t=1715160700\" width=690 height=388 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2928740/extras/88f088156790daf96e25899bb4a48a97.webm?t=1715160700\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2928740/extras/88f088156790daf96e25899bb4a48a97.mp4?t=1715160700\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>Gameplay:</strong><br>The player will have to explore an unfamiliar mansion and uncover the story of a young family that recently moved in here. The player is immersed in an oppressive atmosphere and constantly feels that someone is watching him. Find keys, move through new locations, and discover more details of the frightening story. And yes, try to get out of that scary house.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2928740/extras/f8ef5ed351f4163e0029358377f3b9b9.poster.avif?t=1715160700\" width=690 height=388 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2928740/extras/f8ef5ed351f4163e0029358377f3b9b9.webm?t=1715160700\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2928740/extras/f8ef5ed351f4163e0029358377f3b9b9.mp4?t=1715160700\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>Game Features:</strong><br>• The frightening story.<br>• Atmospheric locations.<br>• The feeling of a familiar place.",
